<!doctype html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><style>
body{font:16px/1.45 system-ui,sans-serif;max-width:960px;margin:32px auto;padding:0 20px;color:#17202a}h1,h2{color:#17365d}.notice{background:#fff4ce;padding:12px;border-left:4px solid #d69e00}.card{border:1px solid #ccd6e0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin:12px 0}.score{font-weight:700}.warning{color:#9c2d18}.muted{color:#59636e}a{color:#1558a6}li{margin:.3em 0}
</style></head><body><h1>Driver Dispatch Intelligence</h1>
<p class="notice"><strong>Independent decision support.</strong> Not affiliated with Uber or Lyft. Scores estimate opportunity from public leading indicators—not future surge pricing. Safety and local/platform rules always take priority.</p>
<h2>Executive summary</h2><p>Week of {{ week_start }}. Best day: <strong>{{ summary.best_day }}</strong>. Best window: <strong>{{ summary.best_window }}</strong>. Recommended total driving time: {{ schedule.total_hours }} hours.</p>
{% if errors %}<p class="warning">Some sources failed; the report is partial.</p><ul>{% for e in errors %}<li>{{ e.source }}: {{ e.message }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>{% endif %}
<h2>Top opportunities</h2>{% for o in top %}<section class="card"><h3>{{ o.event.name }}</h3><p>{{ o.event.start_datetime|fmt }} · {{ o.event.venue_name or o.event.city or 'Location unknown' }}</p><p class="score">Opportunity {{ o.opportunity_score }}/100 · Confidence {{ o.confidence_score }}/100</p>
{% for w in o.demand_windows %}<p><strong>{{ w.kind|title }}:</strong> {{ w.start|time }}–{{ w.end|time }} — {{ w.reason }}</p>{% endfor %}<p>{{ o.staging_guidance }}</p><ul>{% for reason in o.reasons[:5] %}<li>{{ reason }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>{% if o.event.event_url %}<a href="{{ o.event.event_url }}">Source/event page</a>{% endif %} {% if o.event.latitude is not none %}<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query={{ o.event.latitude }},{{ o.event.longitude }}">Map</a>{% endif %}{% for warning in o.warnings %}<p class="warning">{{ warning }}</p>{% endfor %}</section>{% endfor %}
<h2>Recommended weekly schedule</h2>{% for day, items in schedule.by_day.items() %}<h3>{{ day }}</h3>{% for o in items %}<p><strong>{{ o.event.name }}</strong>: {{ o.demand_windows|window_range }} ({{ o.opportunity_score }}/100, confidence {{ o.confidence_score }}/100)</p>{% endfor %}{% else %}<p>No opportunities cleared the configured thresholds. Consider skipping this week.</p>{% endfor %}
<h2>Conflicts and alternatives</h2>{% for c in schedule.conflicts %}<p>{{ c.event }} conflicts with {{ c.conflicts_with }}: {{ c.reason }}</p>{% else %}<p>No material schedule conflicts detected.</p>{% endfor %}
<h2>Events/time windows to avoid or verify</h2>{% for o in suppressed %}<p><strong>{{ o.event.name }}</strong>: {{ o.suppression_reasons|join('; ') }}</p>{% else %}<p>None identified.</p>{% endfor %}
<h2>Weather and airport</h2><p>Weather effects are included when NWS hourly data is available. Severe conditions suppress recommendations when configured risk limits are exceeded.</p><p class="muted">Airport intelligence is not available in V1; no airport opportunity claims are made.</p></body></html>

